title: Launch a awareness program/ series of posts related to scams and security
body: since pancake attracted many new users that doesn't know the basics, i think we should have a awareness program launch with binance or others on twitter to make new people aware of basic scams, like never disclose seed phrases, pishing, letting people know that anyone can list any garbage token etc
